"" Lean."" Whatever that's
supposed to mean.

713
01:20:09,881 --> 01:20:12,175
LEAN是四个字母
"" Lean"" is spelled with four letters.

714
01:20:12,342 --> 01:20:14,594
我想我打了五个
I belieced I punched fice.

715
01:20:16,804 --> 01:20:19,641
喂～那你是说我不会…
Hey, are you saying
I don't know how to--?.

716
01:20:19,807 --> 01:20:23,061
哦～对不起
原来是LEARN(学习),是我错了
I'm sorry. It says ""learn."" My mistake.

717
01:20:23,227 --> 01:20:25,146
学习到了
Lesson learned.

718
01:20:25,313 --> 01:20:26,689
车票
Ticket.

719
01:20:43,498 --> 01:20:44,999
很特别的车票
That is some special ticket.

720
01:20:45,166 --> 01:20:46,668
是的
Sure is.

721
01:20:46,834 --> 01:20:51,130
那…你能“信任”我们
把你安全送回家吗?
So can you count on us
to get you home safe and sound?.

722
01:20:53,216 --> 01:20:54,968
当然
Absolutely.

723
01:20:55,134 --> 01:20:56,636
我…
Me...

724
01:20:57,887 --> 01:20:59,931
还有我的朋友
...and my friends.

725
01:21:02,684 --> 01:21:03,893
车票
Ticket.

726
01:21:12,443 --> 01:21:15,530
是LEAD(铅)比方铅气球
It says ""lead."" Like ""lead balloon.""

727
01:21:15,697 --> 01:21:18,366
我觉得也可以发音“lead”
I beliece it also is pronounced ""lead.""

728
01:21:18,533 --> 01:21:20,493
这个字也是“领”的意思
As in ""leader,"" ""leadership.""

729
01:21:20,660 --> 01:21:22,870
比方领袖,领导…
""Lead the way.""

730
01:21:23,037 --> 01:21:25,248
领…路.谨尊您的领导,夫人
Follow you anywhere, ma'am.

731
01:21:28,126 --> 01:21:29,419
啊，好的
Ah, yes.

732
01:21:29,585 --> 01:21:32,547
充满疑问的小伙子
Young man with all the questions.

733
01:21:33,047 --> 01:21:34,465
车票
Ticket.

734
01:21:44,517 --> 01:21:46,728
写着…
It says--

735
01:21:46,978 --> 01:21:48,605
我不需要知道
It's nothing I need to know.

736
01:21:59,574 --> 01:22:01,951
- 快…拿铃铛给我们看
- 让我们看看铃铛
-Come on, let's see the bell.
-Let's see it.

737
01:22:02,118 --> 01:22:04,829
- 快…拿铃铛给我们看
- 给我们看看铃铛
-Come on, let's see the bell.
-Show us the bell.

738
01:22:04,996 --> 01:22:07,165
让我们看看铃铛
Yeah, let's see the bell.

739
01:22:14,464 --> 01:22:16,174
丢了
It's gone.

740
01:22:17,425 --> 01:22:20,261
- 在哪儿?
- 我弄丢了
-Where is it?.
-I lost it.

741
01:22:20,428 --> 01:22:23,014
我把圣诞老人雪橇上的铃铛弄丢了
I lost the bell from Santa's sleigh.

742
01:22:23,181 --> 01:22:25,016
真的不见了?
It's gone?.

743
01:22:26,351 --> 01:22:27,685
别担心
Don't worry.

744
01:22:27,852 --> 01:22:30,271
- 我们…我们…会找到它
- 是的，我们会找到的
-We'll-- We'll find it.
-Yeah, we'll find it.

745
01:22:30,438 --> 01:22:32,774
对呀,我们帮你,大家都会帮你
Yeah, we'll help you. All of us.

746
01:22:32,941 --> 01:22:35,777
嗯,快,我们现在就去找
Yeah, let's hurry out
and find it right now.

747
01:22:45,286 --> 01:22:47,038
太迟了
It's too late.

748
01:22:48,539 --> 01:22:51,042
真不幸
Gee, that's really too bad.

749
01:22:52,043 --> 01:22:53,711
真的
Really.

750
01:23:08,226 --> 01:23:10,061
我很难过
I'm sorry.

751
01:23:40,925 --> 01:23:44,929
艾布克街11344号
1 1344 Edbrooke.

752
01:23:45,096 --> 01:23:50,560
下一站…艾布克街11344号
Next stop, 1 1 244 Edbrooke.

753
01:23:57,859 --> 01:23:59,777
喂～你要去哪儿?
Hey, where you going?.

754
01:24:00,778 --> 01:24:01,904
回家
Home.

755
01:24:02,071 --> 01:24:05,658
哦,原来,圣诞快乐
Oh, okay. Merry Christmas.

756
01:24:10,705 --> 01:24:13,625
谢谢你,停车让我上来
Thanks for stopping the train for me.

757
01:24:19,464 --> 01:24:21,090
祝你圣诞快乐
Hace a wonderful Christmas.

758
01:24:23,176 --> 01:24:25,678
慢走
Watch your step, please.

759
01:24:27,305 --> 01:24:29,307
圣诞快乐
And merry Christmas.

760
01:24:46,324 --> 01:24:47,617
看
Look.

761
01:24:50,286 --> 01:24:53,164
圣诞老人已经去过他家了
Santa got to Billy's house already.

762
01:24:55,959 --> 01:24:58,711
看…看…圣诞老人来过了
Look, look! Santa got here!

763
01:24:58,878 --> 01:25:00,463
很神奇吧
Isn't that amazing?.

764
01:25:00,630 --> 01:25:02,048
真的很神奇
It is amazing.

765
01:25:09,430 --> 01:25:11,557
真的很神奇
It is amazing.

766
01:25:57,895 --> 01:26:00,189
真难过你的铃铛丢了
I'm sorry about the bell.

767
01:26:00,773 --> 01:26:03,443
是很特别的礼物
It was a really special present.

768
01:26:03,610 --> 01:26:05,361
你知道大家怎么说吗…
Well, you know what they say.

769
01:26:05,528 --> 01:26:07,822
你内心怎么想才是真的
It's the thought that counts.

770
01:26:08,489 --> 01:26:09,949
对
Yeah.

771
01:26:11,117 --> 01:26:13,995
那…再见了
Well, see you.

772
01:26:16,581 --> 01:26:18,124
那…
Well...

773
01:26:18,750 --> 01:26:20,376
再见了
...see you.

774
01:26:21,252 --> 01:26:22,754
再见
See you.

775
01:26:36,559 --> 01:26:39,062
慢走
Watch your step, please.

776
01:26:40,313 --> 01:26:41,564
谢谢你
Thank you.

777
01:26:41,731 --> 01:26:44,275
不对,谢谢你才对
No, thank you.

778
01:26:46,027 --> 01:26:47,820
关於火车…
One thing about trains:

779
01:26:47,987 --> 01:26:50,073
驶去哪儿不重要
It doesn't matter where they're going.

780
01:26:50,239 --> 01:26:54,285
重要的是你想不想搭车
What matters is deciding to get on.

781
01:27:11,260 --> 01:27:12,762
圣…诞…快…乐!
Merry Christmas!

782
01:27:16,474 --> 01:27:17,684
什么?
What?.

783
01:27:18,810 --> 01:27:23,356
圣…诞…快…乐!
Merry Christmas!

784
01:28:31,883 --> 01:28:36,262
醒醒…醒醒…
圣诞老人来过啦…圣诞老人来过啦
Wake up. Wake up.
Santa's been here. Santa's been here.

785
01:28:36,429 --> 01:28:38,097
快呀…快呀
Hurry up. Hurry up!

786
01:28:38,264 --> 01:28:41,601
妈…爸…醒醒…醒醒
Mom, Dad, wake up. Wake up!

787
01:28:41,768 --> 01:28:44,771
圣诞老人来过啦…圣诞老人来过啦
Santa's been here! Santa's been here!

788
01:28:44,938 --> 01:28:48,858
妈…爸…快看
他给了我们这么多礼物
Mom, Dad, look!
He brought us all kinds of stuff!

789
01:28:49,025 --> 01:28:51,569
看…一列火车
Look, a train!

790
01:29:07,961 --> 01:29:13,466
这次是最漂亮最棒的一次圣诞节
This is the beautiful-est,
most wonderful-est Christmas ever.

791
01:29:13,633 --> 01:29:15,927
等等…看
Wait. Look.

792
01:29:17,220 --> 01:29:19,097
还有一个
Here's one more.

793
01:29:20,640 --> 01:29:22,517
上面有你的名字
Has your name on it.

794
01:29:51,421 --> 01:29:53,923
在我雪橇座位底下找到的
found this on the seat of my sleigh.

795
01:29:54,090 --> 01:29:56,759
你最好把破口袋补好
Better fix that hole in your pocket.

796
01:29:56,926 --> 01:29:58,177
圣先生赠
Mr. C.

797
01:30:08,509 --> 01:30:11,672
Oh, what a beautiful bell.
Who's it from?.

798
01:30:09,355 --> 01:30:11,482
好漂亮的铃铛,谁送的?

799
01:30:11,649 --> 01:30:13,693
- 圣诞老人
- 圣诞老人?
-Santa.
-Santa?.

800
01:30:13,860 --> 01:30:15,486
真的!?
Really?.

801
01:30:16,529 --> 01:30:18,948
- 可惜了
- 这是什么?
-Oh, that's too bad.
-What's this?.

802
01:30:19,991 --> 01:30:21,492
坏了
Broken.

803
01:30:22,619 --> 01:30:24,787
真可惜坏了
Sorry about that, sport.

804
01:30:29,334 --> 01:30:32,462
孩子们快吧,我们不想迟到
Come on, kids. We don't wanna be late.

805
01:30:40,511 --> 01:30:44,015
曾几何时,我大部分的朋友
都能听到铃声
At one time, most of my friends
could hear the bell.

806
01:30:44,182 --> 01:30:48,227
但是大家过去的这些年头
都已悄悄逝去
But as years passed,
it fell silent for all of them.

807
01:30:48,394 --> 01:30:53,691
甚至某年莎拉也突然
再也听不见甜美的铃声
Even Sarah found, one Christmas, that she
could no longer hear its sweet sound.

808
01:30:53,858 --> 01:30:55,526
现在我长大了…
Though I've grown old...

809
01:30:55,693 --> 01:30:58,071
还是能听到铃声
... the bell still rings for me.

810
01:30:58,237 --> 01:31:02,325
就像所有相信圣诞节的人一样
As it does for all who truly believe.

811
01:31:05,828 --> 01:31:08,957
谢谢观赏

